8-09T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"要佢執柒咗佢就係個目標！由我地唔撚食做起！<br />\n食壽司燒肉打邊爐，大把選擇好食過佢！<br />\n自己唔好食，勸喻身邊所有親戚朋友姨媽菇姐唔好食！唔好助紂為虐！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一。養心殿老闆專講風涼話！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220224/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220224/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二。剽竊台灣品牌，台灣毫不知情</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/430670604455555/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F430670604455555%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=03ba180d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/430670604455555/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三。高空擲物，員工沖出黎拆RB</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378494/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378494/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四。八號風波</span></span><br />\n做飲食八號大波要開無可厚非。但係喂，我屌你老母咩？洗唔洗咁撚串？<br />\n【颱風山竹】火鍋店養心殿預告8號風球照營業　fb回應釀關公災難<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/235768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F235768&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=6e3f24cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/235768</a><br />\n<br />\n淆底聲明，喂，屌你老母咩，柒到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1312429/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1312429/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n撐警？屌你老母！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1313627/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1313627/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n養心殿有以下幾間餐廳品牌<br />\n養心麵<br />\n養心殿涮涮鍋<br />\n靖壽司 Omakase<br />\n嘉 日本燒肉<br />\n靠炆雞<br />\n彤Bar&amp;Lounge (尖沙咀棉登徑11月底營業)<br />\n老闆嘉輝有黑社會背景，深藍撐警<br />\n唔好比錢佢賺！！！<br />\n<br />\n資料有Fc有冇Fc，自己判斷。但我就一定唔撚食"},{"pid":"da29d6a57a516176852edb2b76301efd1a516eda","tid":1385820,"uid":192311,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"要佢執柒咗佢就係個目標！由我地唔撚食做起！<br />\n食壽司燒肉打邊爐，大把選擇好食過佢！<br />\n自己唔好食，勸喻身邊所有親戚朋友姨媽菇姐唔好食！唔好助紂為虐！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一。養心殿老闆專講風涼話！</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1220224/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1220224/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二。剽竊台灣品牌，台灣毫不知情</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/430670604455555/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F430670604455555%2F&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=03ba180d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/430670604455555/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三。高空擲物，員工沖出黎拆RB</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1378494/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1378494/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">四。八號風波</span></span><br />\n做飲食八號大波要開無可厚非。但係喂，我屌你老母咩？洗唔洗咁撚串？<br />\n【颱風山竹】火鍋店養心殿預告8號風球照營業　fb回應釀關公災難<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/235768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F235768&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=6e3f24cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/235768</a><br />\n<br />\n淆底聲明，喂，屌你老母咩，柒到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1312429/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1312429/page/